# Empty publish directory for the gateway Netlify site.
#
# This directory exists so `publish = "site"` in
# `netlify/gateway/netlify.toml` resolves to a real
# directory. The site serves no static content; the
# gateway's only HTTP surface is the `/private/v1/*`
# function routes. The .gitkeep file is the only file
# ever committed to this directory.
